{"tid":1720773,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[改圖] 見到呢條8婆臭雞就火起","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:44.000Z","uid":72147,"like":20,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"748e31e3cf6c47287483dc94ff4c47e822a8e73f","tid":1720773,"uid":72147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFVOfRq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFVOfRq.jpg&h=1c0c14cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係呢條8婆臭雞<br />\n扮乜撚野蒙眼? 個天砰明顯傾斜到仆街啦<br />\n日日俾人瘋狂抽插中出既臭雞都扮女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想有人改圖恥笑條臭西<br />\n<br />\n[QUOTE[]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蒙上雙眼是代表法庭處理案件時不會理會出席的訴訟各方的身分。在法庭里，無論任何人、任何機構，都不會因為他們／它們是甚麼人或甚麼機構，也不會因為他們／它們代表甚麼利益或團體，而享有優勢或遭受不利的對待。</span>這也就是我剛才強調的平等概念的體現。法庭內，沒有人會單純因為其地位而處於優勢，這點不難領會。然而，在法律面前，沒有人應因為他本身是甚麼人或他所代表的利益或團體而遭受不利的對待，這一點卻往往未如上述那一點般為人所理解。<br />\n<br />\n[UNQUOTE]<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/society/zn4bnoq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fsociety%2Fzn4bnoq.html&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=c9a2d18b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/society/zn4bnoq.html</a><br />\n<br />\n搵多張條臭西唔同角度既圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n含撚啦8婆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tUbX21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tUbX21.jpg&h=cb269990&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"380bf42b35a4fe7a52911c85e56c79519abd3a0e","tid":1720773,"uid":63843,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:59:49.000Z","msg":"細個果陣我仲以為個意思係&quot;天無眼&quot;咁解"},{"pid":"ee32fc9aee479f2efc99c7757cf99c2f6ec7c1a1","tid":1720773,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi